{"tid":1771743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中大出咗驗身報告","createTime":"2019-12-06T05:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T05:47:45.000Z","uid":314354,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f673fd8bb4921b205ed965b8fb93646ee7a915d4","tid":1771743,"uid":314354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:40:19.000Z","msg":"話說段校長派咗啲人去檢查中大校園入面嘅水同泥土有冇有害物質<br />\n<br />\n而家出咗一部分嘅化驗報告<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cuhk.edu.hk/chinese/whats-on/focus/campus-env-result.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fchinese%2Fwhats-on%2Ffocus%2Fcampus-env-result.html&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=2079d3dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cuhk.edu.hk/chinese/whats-on/focus/campus-env-result.html</a><br />\n<br />\n已經有結果嗰啲地方睇落去正正常常<br />\n除咗夏鼎基個男厠二噁英有啲高<br />\n但係最令人關注嘅二號橋夏鼎基其他樣本未出報告<br />\n<br />\n如果有相關行業嘅人士，可唔可以幫手睇下個準則係咪符合國際標準<br />\n<br />\n大家要繼續留意佢之後放出嚟嘅報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e704194424d13cd99610d8cdb42b06b2a843aef","tid":1771743,"uid":314354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:41:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e0788d214cbb7e2ee5432c987d68a2f1452122b","tid":1771743,"uid":314354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"ec4c112c195db5fef7f2b3a0a2106671ebb74f68","tid":1771743,"uid":314354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f7008d67c9848adb38643ed97211b5566a369ca","tid":1771743,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n【上個post無人理】全港最大Fact check 平台正式推出啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1767630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1767630</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"83a1ece15d85ccf8a3d5f6774de03e8df2f1fb79","tid":1771743,"uid":314354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201